            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> the most dangerous option is probably 'filetype'\n\nWhat makes 'filetype' dangerous? Is the risk that a modeline could set certain \"special\" filetypes like `qf`, `pager`, etc? Because if so, we could just blacklist those.\n\nIf the issue is something general with not wanting modelines to load ftplugins, then I suppose it can't be helped. I'm not sure what the risk would be exactly though.",
